item.description:

sanga282:

a general music tracker, and a picture of the amount of music would be apprecaited, as a standard user you can only upload packs but if youi have a lot of music you should apply to upload individual albums as well. Its not as good as say waffles or what but i have no invites for either of them my ratio on both is insufficient

If it helps I was in waffles and both what.cd and (I think what.cd’s sister site) metalbits.org before I got banned for being inactive(suppose seeding doesn’t count as activity :o).

Once I get my other pc setup I will be downloading a lot more music off of usenet. (Will be seeding off of this).
